    "description": "Bounty Star 是一款越肩视角的 3D 动作游戏，结合了机甲战斗以及可自由定制的耕作和基地建设。玩家扮演一个名叫 Clem 的退役士兵，她尽管伤痕累累，但战斗力仍然十分强大。她是一个退伍老兵，也是极有才华的战士和专家机甲师。Clem 试图摆脱过去的愧疚和耻辱，成为无际赤地中一股正义力量。无际赤地是发生在美国西南部的末日后情景。<br><br>主要特色：<br><br>可自定义的机甲动作<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497430/extras/581f579545dc1a5fc125ff52cfe7cc9d.poster.avif?t=1761224385\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497430/extras/581f579545dc1a5fc125ff52cfe7cc9d.webm?t=1761224385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497430/extras/581f579545dc1a5fc125ff52cfe7cc9d.mp4?t=1761224385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你操纵沙漠猛禽 MKII，一款极为强大的机甲。它是一种高度可定制的战斗机器，可以配备各种攻击系统：重型、高功率近战武器、蒸汽动力液压攻城武器、爆炸性火器等等。它还可以配备各种防御系统；高速推进器、冲刺助推器、防暴盾牌等。<br><br>成为一个赏金猎人<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497430/extras/f86919231edec4981f669b922ffee688.poster.avif?t=1761224385\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497430/extras/f86919231edec4981f669b922ffee688.webm?t=1761224385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497430/extras/f86919231edec4981f669b922ffee688.mp4?t=1761224385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>无际赤地是一个富饶的农业和商业混合的地带，充斥着暴力罪犯和危险的野兽。政府将执法外包给像 Clem 这样的专业人士，这些赏金猎人可以追捕目标到天涯海角。她将在无际赤地之上披荆斩棘，一路搏杀，并在时机合适的时候处理留下的痕迹。<br><br>修复并升级你的基地<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497430/extras/7ce13f5201139592cb57ef4779717328.poster.avif?t=1761224385\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497430/extras/7ce13f5201139592cb57ef4779717328.webm?t=1761224385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497430/extras/7ce13f5201139592cb57ef4779717328.mp4?t=1761224385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Clem 走进了一个与世隔绝、破旧不堪的仓库，这里是一个不错的作战基地，勉强也能称之为家。在这里修建供水和供电线路，种植作物和烹煮食物，生产用于战斗的弹药和燃料，还有饲养动物。这个破旧的废墟有很大的潜力，但它必须与 Clem 一起成长。",
